The company&#39;s &quot;risk warning&quot; states: in connection with the Hungarian Guard&#39;s activities, the greatest political risk is that &quot;by exacerbating the already existing ethnic tensions between the Roma and non-Roma population in Hungary, violent ethnic clashes may occur in a short time&quot;.
The main reason is that the political strategy of the Hungarian Guard is probably aimed at provoking such an action - adds the research institute.
