The emphasis on civility and the form of the association in the case of these groups therefore not only serves to avoid the legal pitfalls of judicial registration, but is also a political strategy.
According to the analysis, the activities of the Hungarian Guard are a risk-increasing factor also in terms of neighborly relations.
